{"tid":2278154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得cctvb 真理部為左民眾安全先作新聞係 用心良苦","createTime":"2020-11-09T03:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:08:35.000Z","uid":25240,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc7f65a7cb61b273f5232620bdc86242f63a5f6","tid":2278154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"大家都怪錯左tvb真理部<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JApOWem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJApOWem.png&h=bc9e59ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月11日葉建源話組織罷課 <br />\n真理部成員即收左枝咪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgossmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqgossmd.jpg&h=88ab0b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高清圖版<br />\n<br />\n一開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHwrGhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHwrGhM.png&h=1ef5590c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一講罷課之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm0TmhT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm0TmhT.png&h=3972599a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日元朗黑社會無差別攻擊市民改成「有大量人聚集」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi1K56x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi1K56x.jpg&h=2d723132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年8月5日將北角黑社會打人在先故意剪走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxVG8fR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxVG8fR.jpg&h=98e447b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年10月1日 健仔心口中槍 班狗阻礙急救改成「防暴幫健仔急救」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOKs3PB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOKs3PB.jpg&h=ca27d6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年10月6日 女義士被的士狗故意車斷雙腳講成「不小心進入行人路被圍毆」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYhBW7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYhBW7Q.jpg&h=65c16675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月3日趙家賢被大陸佬咬甩一隻耳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZuy7np.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZuy7np.jpg&h=e54dccbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年8月31日 推大肚婆落地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Zpjit5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Zpjit5.jpg&h=73d1a4c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e463593e81b23bd3f6db334fc36cbc1cf23f607b","tid":2278154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cacd4e87a18d30ee4e493c271333d6022498cd","tid":2278154,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"939880b17b7fc8fe2f0e0eae82893a0b44c52937","tid":2278154,"uid":77180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"梁啟智呢d左膠唔理journalistic ethics<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對左膠有利就okay"},{"pid":"2949c71856f9da4e738f30148368634351157e65","tid":2278154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e463593e81b23bd3f6db334fc36cbc1cf23f607b","tid":2278154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c802dd20713759b8d87cb22ad87f04492036ea","tid":2278154,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"